<item>
            <title>[LU-10640] ha.sh improvement: add stat(2) check</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10640</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ha.sh script proposed improvement:&lt;br/&gt;
In each load iteration check for all created directories that ls&apos; long format does not contain &apos;?&apos; which could happen when stat(2) called by ls fails.&lt;br/&gt;
The stat(2) failure may be caused by the missing objects as well as by number of other reasons.&lt;br/&gt;
If &apos;?&apos; is found sleep for several minutes and repeat the check.&lt;br/&gt;
Exit with error if &apos;?&apos; still exists after second check.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
